Product Name: AI-Sonic OD-52W vanntett inne/ute høyttaler i kabinett
Product Discription:
AI-Sonic OD-52W is a weatherproof box speaker. Speaker has 5,25" midrange/woofer that is optimized to give good bass response and clear midrange in a sealed enclosure. Weatherproof Mylar-dome tweeter takes care of the higher frequencies. Thanks to Finnish engineering and carefully selected components these speakers have outstanding sound quality in their price class. OD-52W is very good choice to boat, terrace, public spaces and works well indoors and outdoors. You can even use them in sauna if you want. Waterproof ABS-enclosure is delivered with installation components and grilles. Logo stickers are in the package, you can put them in correct position depending the mounting position of speaker or leave them unattached if you want. 

Technical data 

Woofer 5,25" 
Tweeter 13mm dome 
Impedance 4 Ohm 
Frequency response 68-21kHz 
Recommended amplifier 10-110W RMS 
Sensitivity 91dB 1m 2,83V 
Weight 2kg each 
UV-protected 
Splash waterproof 
Height 233mm 
Width 185mm 
Depth 165mm 
Depth with bracket 190mm

Do you want an amplifier to feed your speakers on terrace, sauna, bathroom or garage? Or more powerfull amplifier for your computer speakers? Or build a simple sound system to bedroom, kids room, student flat or perhaps your home gym at the basement? Ai-Sonic BT-A255 is a perfect solution if you want to listen music wirelessly via Bluetooth. Small physical size makes it easy to install virtually anywhere. Other sources are USB and RCA/AuxIn analog line input. You can connect flash drive to USB and switch songs with remote included. Remote need sight to amp, it works with IR. Via RCA-input you can listen to any source that has line output. WIth included 1.5 metres RCA/AuxIn cable you can change it to AuxIn. The best feature is Bluetooth 5.0 that gives you freedom to listen your music wirelessly from allmost any mobile devices. Power of this amp is enough to play any regular speakers even with loud volumes. You also can play loud, since output is allway distortion free! Amplifier reduces level automatically when signal is in danger to get distorted. Automatic control also reduces level when amplifier gets too hot. Speaker outputs have short cut protection. If speaker cables are harmed, protection circuit shuts outputs instantly. If you want even more power, you can bridge this amp and get more juice out of it ( minimum impedance 8 Ohms when bridged). Bluetooth range is normally 20 metres in open space.

The VO-B4 is the follow up to the very popular VO-B3 super tweeter. When comparing the VO-B3 to the VO-B4, customers will notice increased frequency response, efficiency, and max power handling. This was accomplished by using a larger diaphragm and voice coupled to a stronger motor. 
The VO-B4 is truly a high-output, PA-Style, bullet tweeter designed for the mobile environment. The VO-B4’s custom CNC machined body and die-cast motor are designed to be as short as possible to allow for easy mounting in door panels and motorcycle applications. 
The B4’s horn body is designed to project a wider field of sound in close proximity when compared to similarly styled tweeters. Another unique feature of the VO-B4 is its dual mounting options. The installer has the option to flush mount with the trim bezel and back nut, or for more space-constrained installs it can be top mounted using the machined screw holes in the tweeter body.

Testreferat fra Car & HiFi 4/08: 
The music almost "jumps at you" when playing these speakers... It is unbelievable how natural it sounds... if you open your eyes you are disappointed, because you can not see the singer you think standing in front of you when listening to his voice... You can easily imagine how big or small the room has been, where the music has been recorded... it is all clear and perfect, so you have a "picture" in your head... It takes a while to get used to the sound of this speaker system and due to the pretty low Qts of the midrange (Qts 0.29) some will miss a little of the very low bass, but you get the most precise kick bass ever... High-End listeners will smile when listening to these speakers...

En passiv påkostet og avansert delefilter følger med høyttalersystemet. Det komplette Gladen Zero Pro høyttalersystemet er designet og bygget i Tyskland.

PS 165 SF er produsert i Frankrike på Focal sin fabrikk i St-Etienne. Det inneholder essensen av Focals nyeste teknologier for å levere ytelse og pålitelighet. Den eksklusive Slatefiber membranen bidrar til å skape et rikt lydbilde. Standarddimensjonene på 6 1/2" (165 mm) og smart design betyr at den kan installeres i de fleste kjøretøy på markedet. Sist, men ikke minst, gir dens høye følsomhet jevn forsterkning. PS 165 SF kan kobles direkte til den originale bilradioen eller brukes med en forsterker for å få mest mulig ut av høyttalerene. I tillegg til å levere god ytelse, er settene også enkle å installere. Mid-Woofer:

Høyeste lydkvalitet 
Med S-seriens høyttalere blir hver tur en spesiell lydopplevelse. Det sofistikerte designet og bruken av de nyeste teknologiene garanterer utmerkede lydegenskaper med fyldig bass, nøyaktige mellomtoner og krystallklar diskant. 

Klassisk design 
I tillegg til de utmerkede lydegenskapene, imponerer S 62C.2 også med sin tidløse elegante design. Spesielt det gjennomsiktige "Flex-delefilteret" med sine høykvalitetskomponenter og det edle aluminiumshuset til diskanthøyttaleren gjør dette systemet til en ekte fryd for øyet. 

Enkel integrasjon 
Den sofistikerte designen med lave installasjonsdybder, et avtakbart hus til diskanthøyttaleren og den svært kompakte og innovative "Flex-delefilteret" gir mye mer frihet når det gjelder tilkobling og installasjon – selv på spesielt begrenset plass. I tillegg gir den en enkel kabling, takket være Plug & Play-tilkoblinger mellom de enkelte komponentene. 

Maksimal fleksibilitet – "Flex-delefilter" 
Den nye "Flex-delefilteret" er ikke bare et visuelt høydepunkt, den innebærer også et par tekniske finesser. For å redusere dimensjonene drastisk kan kretskortet også monteres uten hus i et medfølgende skum, og det kan deles i to deler for separat installasjon (f.eks. diskanthøyttaler i A-stolpe, basshøyttaler i døren). I tillegg til en 3-trinns diskantnivåjustering og Plug & Play-kabeltilkoblinger, er delefilteret også utstyrt med skruterminaler for enda mer fleksibilitet når du kobler til med dine egne høyttalerkabler.

The D Class 6.5 Component set consists of high tech, high fidelity drivers designed for the listener wanting to go well beyond the standard factory upgrade. 

Woofer: 

Our focus on sound quality starts with precision motor assemblies. The machined magnet gaps driven with high energy strontium magnets provide strong output from a compact design. We incorporated distortion reducing copper shorting rings for flux modulation and inductance control. The aluminum mid woofer cones achieve wide bandwidth and efficient energy transfer to the air. The compressed rubber surrounds are durable and have been optimized for light weight to increase sensitivity. 

Tweeter: 

The tweeter side of the D Class component sets is our T2a 25mm ultra-light diaphragm tweeter. This new diaphragm is less than 0.003 of an inch thick; that’s almost nothing of a mm. This proprietary fabric is so thin it’s virtually see through, well, actually it is see through. The ultra-light dome is coupled to a low-distortion, neo motor with flush/surface mounting hardware and metal grill options. 

Crossover: 

The 2-way crossover features low distortion coils and metalized polypropylene caps that pass the source without degradation. The D Class components are purposefully built, enthusiast quality sets — everything you need for great sound and nothing you don’t.

Woofer: 

The 6.5-inch woofer features an injection molded poly cone, rubber surround, and rigid steel frame. Høyttalerelementene bruker Polyglass-teknologi, som gir veldefinert mellomtone og bass. Aluminium invertert dome diskant, en Focal teknologi, gir perfekt diskantgjengivelse med meget god spredning av lyden. Dette settet er designet for kjøretøy som har separat diskant.

Gladen Zero Pro-serien gjør toppmoderne mobil lydteknologi fra serier som Gladen aerospace og Gladen Pro-serien tilgjengelig for en bredere målgruppe. Den innovative delefilteret muliggjør individuell og optimal kabling av de enkelte systemhøyttalerne. Dette garanterer en perfekt tildeling av høyttalerne i kjøretøyet ditt. 

High End semi aktivt system som består av en 165 mm basshøyttaler, 80mm mellomtone og en 28 mm dome diskanthøyttaler. 
Mellomtonen har en faseplugg i midten. Akustisk sørger fasepluggen for at lyden fra membranen ikke reflekteres ved polkjernen. Uten dette kan faseskift føre til kanselleringer som er merkbare som et fall i mellomtonen. 
En passiv påkostet og avansert delefilter følger med høyttalersystemet. Det komplette Gladen Zero Pro høyttalersystemet er designet og bygget i Tyskland.

De fint oppløselige silkediskanthøyttalerne kan brukes veldig universelt på grunn av deres kabinettdesign og legger alle lyddetaljene inn i kjøretøyet ditt.

The D Class Coaxial Speakers are high tech, high fidelity speakers designed for the listener wanting to go well beyond the standard factory upgrade. Woofer: For the D Class speakers, our focus on sound quality started with precision motor assemblies. The machined magnet gaps are driven with high-energy strontium magnets providing strong output from a compact design. We also incorporated distortion reducing copper shorting rings for flux modulation and inductance control. The cones are made of a rigid pulp with acoustic treatment applied to the front, reducing cone breakup while providing water/humidity resistance. The compressed rubber surrounds are ultra durable and have been optimized for light weight to increase sensitivity. Tweeter: The tweeter side of the D Class coaxial is our neo driven T2 25mm ultra-light diaphragm tweeter. Its diaphragm is less than 0.003 of an inch thick that’s almost nothing of a mm. The proprietary dome fabric is so thin it’s virtually see through, well, actually it is see through. The ultra-light dome is coupled to a low-distortion neo motor. We also used a high tolerance mylar capacitor for the built in high pass crossover allowing the T2 tweeter to effortlessly exude crystal clear highs. The D Class coaxials are designed with the same exotic features as esoteric separates at a price that fits any enthusiast’s budget. Why settle for OEM sound when a DD upgrade is so easy?

Medfølger: 2 x Plug & Play connectors for original BMW cable harness 

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
The BMW-specific baskets and Plug & Play connectors allow a fast and easy installation into the original mounting positions of all BMW model ranges with under-seat subwoofers. 
Nevertheless, these subwoofers are also perfectly qualified for universal applications. Thanks to the very low mounting depth, extremely compact sealed enclosures are no problem at all whereas the oversized 1.7” / 42.5 mm voice coil assures high power handling. 
Furthermore, the special speaker connector with its gold-plated screw terminals allows two different configurations and therefore flexible connection options. With the ex works installed connection bracket the subwoofer has an impedance of 1 x 4 Ohms, otherwise each voice coil can be driven individually (impedance 2 x 2 Ohms) and allows perfect combination with MATCH Plug & Play amplifiers. 
No matter if these subwoofers are used as bass upgrade in your BMW or as problem-solver in small sub enclosures, they will definitely add loads of powerful bass for musical enjoyment..

The 9900s are the go to subwoofers for the demanding bassaholic with a profound interest in physics. Entertaining minds will revel in the endless system design possibilities deliverable with these precision low-frequency devices. Originally coined The Beast, the 9900s first appeared on the market in the early 2000s. It took a brief hiatus, but now it’s back and more beastly than ever. The latest iteration was developed in response to the recent explosion in ultra-low-frequency music. These subwoofers were designed to provide long-term power handling, with accuracy, and high excursion capabilities. It’s been optimized for a 1500 – 2500 watt power band with the ability able to handle bursts of up to 10,000 watts. One look at the 9900 motor and you see why we call it the beast. It boasts 3 inches of magnet cross-section, over a 10" OD, and weighs in at 70 pounds (motor only). The traditionally tight DD magnet gap drives a 4" flat wound aluminum voice coil to a peak excursion in excess of 3 inches while keeping enough turns in the gap to maintain power and control. The 9900 Series features our Evolution Subwoofer Package (ESP). ESP equipped drivers sport larger diameter suspensions and deeper frames than standard subs and exclusive surround and cone designs. ESP subs are truly built to maximize performance in their designated size class. The 9900 Series comes standard with an oversized dry finish black composite dust cap, red logo, and treated pulp cone, but it can be optioned out with alternative composite dust caps, composite cones, powder coated frames, supercharging, and a multitude of logo options to give your sub a personalized look and/or added performance for a specific application.

Utfordringen var å oppnå et perfekt samspill mellom høyttalerkomponentene under stort sett ugunstige høyttalerinstallasjonsforhold. 
Alle høyttalerne i Gladen One serien ble testet og optimalt innstilt under reelle forhold i bilen, i vårt interne testlaboratorium. På slutten av utviklingen har alle høyttalere fra Gladen ikke bare gjennomgått en rekke parameter- og frekvensresponstester, men har også blitt finjustert av våre lydteknikere

Product Information: Plug and Play 8" basskit til BMW
Product Discription:
De fleste av BMW lydanlegg kan ikke oppfylle de krevende forventningene til sofistikerte musikkelskere, og er heller ikke i stand til å nå oppnå høye lydtrykk. Dette er årsaken til at markedet tilbyr mer kraftige høyttalere som passer i originalplasseringene - såkalte "plug and play" løsninger . 

Ground Zero introduserer GZCS 200BMW -SW, en ny subwoofer som er perfekt tilpasset, har meget bra lydkvalitet og kan spille skikkelig høyt. Den kan bli montert uten noen endringer i BMW ledningene og erstatter de svake fabrikkhøyttalerne. Basselementet på 20 cm / 8" er optimalisert ved hjelp av GZ sitt Klippel® målesystem. Den har 2 ohm talespole og kraftig og kompakt neodymiummagnet. 

Subwooferen er egnet for alle BMW E6 , 7 , 8 og 9 modeller så vel som for F-serien. Den passer også de nyeste Mini F-modellene. 

Impedans 4 Ohm 
Maks effekt: 160W

Medfølger: 2 x Plug & Play connectors for original BMW cable harness 

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
The BMW-specific baskets and Plug & Play connectors allow a fast and easy installation into the original mounting positions of all BMW model ranges with under-seat subwoofers. 
Nevertheless, these subwoofers are also perfectly qualified for universal applications. Thanks to the very low mounting depth, extremely compact sealed enclosures are no problem at all whereas the oversized 1.7” / 42.5 mm voice coil assures high power handling. 
Furthermore, the special speaker connector with its gold-plated screw terminals allows two different configurations and therefore flexible connection options. With the ex works installed connection bracket the subwoofer has an impedance of 1 x 4 Ohms, otherwise each voice coil can be driven individually (impedance 2 x 2 Ohms) and allows perfect combination with MATCH Plug & Play amplifiers. 
No matter if these subwoofers are used as bass upgrade in your BMW or as problem-solver in small sub enclosures, they will definitely add loads of powerful bass for musical enjoyment..

Product Name: MATCH MEC BT HD UP 7BMW / DSP Bluetooth modul -ny HD versjon
Product Discription:
Trådløs lydstrømming i HD-kvalitet via Bluetooth® 
Utvidelseskortet BT HD utvider din HELIX-enhet med en Bluetooth®-lydstrømmefunksjon i HD-kvalitet med opptil 576 kbps og 24 Bit/48 kHz samplingsfrekvens takket være BT5.0+EDR-standarden. Modulen støtter lydkodeken SBC, AAC, aptX og aptX HD. I tillegg er modulen utstyrt med en optisk digital utgang i SPDIF-format. 

 
Den økte dataoverføringen med BT5.0 standarden i kombinasjon med DSP PC-Tool-programvaren V5 (kommer i begynnelsen av 2022) og en PC med trådløs Bluetooth®-teknologi tillater trådløs konfigurasjon av alle DSP-enheter med ACO-plattform. En tungvint tilkobling via USB-kabel er nå en saga blott. 

 
Takket være støtten til Qualcomm® aptX™ HD-lydkodeken, er trådløs og konstant lydoverføring i HD-kvalitet mulig. Videre tillater den direkte signaloverføringen av de digitale signalene fra BT HD-modulen til DSP uten ekstra AD-DA-konvertering tapsfri lydbehandling og dermed enestående lydytelse. 

 
MEC BT HD støtter kontrollkommandoer som avspilling/pause, spor fremover/tilbake, koble til, paring og frakobling av en tilkoblet DSP-fjernkontroll (f.eks. CONDUCTOR og DIRECTOR). DIRECTOR-displayet viser deg også gjeldende artist og tittel samt den for øyeblikket brukte lydkodeken. 

 
For sømløs installasjon er selvfølgelig et enhetsspesifikt sidepanel og en høykvalitets antenne for maksimal overføringskvalitet inkludert i leveringen.

Product Information: 8 kanals klasse D med 10 kanals DSP
Product Discription:
Mosconi Pico forsterkerne representerer fremtiden for oppgradering av lyden i dagens biler. De meget kompakte forsterkerene kombinerer toppmoderne høyhastighets digitale forsterkere, smarte strømforsyninger og innovative DSP-funksjoner. 
Dette resulterer i høy effekt med minst mulig strømforbruk, som er et grunnleggende krav for moderne og også elektriske kjøretøy. 
DSP-versjonene (Digital Signal Processor) tilbyr en rekke utstyr og utvidelsesmuligheter, som Bluetooth-lydstrømming i høyoppløselig lydformat. 
Med de valgfrie OEM-kabelsettene er en perfekt og ikke destruktiv integrering av Mosconi Pico-ene i bilen mulig. 

 
Kraftig DSP-forsterker optimalisert for fabrikkradioer. Seks analoge innganger opptil 30V, fleksibel ruting, 3x inngangs-EQ og forsinkelse. Med 4x50 watt + 4x 90 watt er den ideell for aktive og semi-aktive systemer, samt klassisk front+bak+sub-applikasjon. I brokoblet modus på kanal 5 - 8 har man hele 480W tilgjengelig fordelt på en eller flere basshøyttalere. Med to digitale innganger (SP-Dif og BT+) og to behandlede linjeutganger er den klar for fremtiden. 

 
Høyeffektive PWM utgangstrinn med den raskeste bærefrekvensen i verden i dag (>2MHz). Moduleringen gjøres uten DAC direkte fra 48kHz TDM-signalet til DSP, og dermed går støygulvet til null og THD+N ~0,02% / 1W. 

RMS utgangseffekt @ 4 Ohm: 
4x 50 Watt (kanal 1-4) 3 Ohm stabil (kan ikke brokobles!) 
4x 90 Watt (kanal 5-8) 2 Ohm stabil (kan brokobles) 
4x 120 Watt (kanal 5-8) @ 2 Ohm 
4x 50 Watt + 2x 240 Watt (brokoblet kanal 5+6/7+8)) 

Linjeutgang : 2 x 2Vrms 
Inngangsignal volt: 0,3 - 15 V 
Total effektivitet: >80 % 
Auto-On (kun høynivå: AV - BTL 
Fysiske mål: 150 x 160 x 46 mm 
Nettovekt 1050 gram 

INNGANGER: 
4 x analoge balanserte innganger (Høynivå) opp til 30V. 
4 x valgbare analoge innganger (Høynivå / lavnivå) 
1x digital inngang SP-Dif optisk (8kHz - 96kHz samplingsfrekvens) 
1x Bluetooth port med SP-Dif - TTL (8kHz - 96kHz, feks. for Mos_BTS Bluetooth streamingmodul) 
Bluetooth digital audio port (BT+) 
(fleksibel 8kHz - 384kHz synkron digital inngang for lydkilder med 2 - 16 kanaler, direkte DSP-tilgang uten jitter, f.eks. for MOS BTS-LD4C BT streamingmodul eller utvidede analoge innganger) 

PROGRAMVARE: 
3 x 9-bånds parametriske inngangs-EQ (de-equalisering) 
6 x inngangsforsinkelse 0 - 3ms / 0,01ms (de-forsinkelse) 
10 x inngangsnivåkontroll digital (signalbehandling) 
Fleksibel mikser for signalruting 
(Sideseparert, kan summere og trekke fra, 10 innganger til 4x2 utgangsgrupper) 
6 x 30 bånd eller 4x30 bånd + 2x15 bånd gruppe EQ 
(parametrisk, relativ fase forblir stabil) 
10 x 10-bånds utgangsfiltre 
HighPass / LowPass / HighShelf / LowShelf / Notch / Allpass 1. + 2. orden / Speaker-EQ) 
10 x høyttalerforsinkelse 0 - 12ms, 0,02ms 
10 x høyttalerfasebryter 

KONTROLL: 
1 x fjernkontroll (analog, for RTC.2 Poti fjernkontroll) 
1 x Bluetooth-kontrollport (Tilkobling MOS-BT3.0 (App-kontroll), RC-Can (CAN-Bus-kontroll), MOS_USB2.0 (programmeringsdongel) 
1 x fjernkontroll ut, 1x fjernkontroll inn, automatisk fjernkontroll for tilkobling på høyt nivå. 
Tilkoblinger med MOLEX® pluggkontakter. 
Svært liten størrelse med lav varmeutvikling, godt egnet for montering bak paneler. 

DSP: 
912 MHz, 32-bits lydport, 64-bit kjerne. 
Double Precision 56Bit filterberegning. 
6144 SIMD-instruksjoner samplingsfrekvens ved 48 kHz. 
ASRC-er fra 1:8 opp til 7,75:1 forhold og 139 dB DNR.

Meget høy kvalitet høy/lav-adapter fra Tyske GLADEN. 
For tilkobling av forsterker til en Radio/CD uten linjeutganger 
Remote utgang (gir et remote signal som trengs for å slå på en forsterker) 
Slår seg automatisk på og av via høyttalersignal 
Forgyllte tilkoblinger 
Meget høy kvalitet høy/lav-adapter fra Tyske GLADEN. 
Auto start med remote utgang 
Galvanisk isolasjon 
Forhindrer jordsløyfe og RF støy 
Fjerngenerering via BTL eller signaldeteksjon 

I dag er høy-lav adaptere nesten utelukkende basert på elektroniske operative forsterkerkretser. Disse elektroniske omformerne opererer svært lineært med høy båndbredde. Disse fordelene kan føre til problemer under ugunstige omstendigheter, spesielt med OEM klasse D-forsterkere er en induktiv belastning med filtereffekt det bedre valget. På grunn av kretsløp er ikke elektroniske konverterere helt isolert fra bakken, noe som kan føre til at forsterkeren slås av i sensitiv OEM-diagnostikk 
Gladen HTL10 Høy/Low converter gir komplett galvanisk isolasjon på inn- og utgangssider og begrenser overføringen til hørbar rekkevidde. Den filtrerer restene av klasse-D bærefrekvensen fra signalet, og avlaster dermed påfølgende komponenter og gjør reproduksjon mer behagelig og "varmere" totalt sett.

Ekstra info: 
- High quality spare wheel active subwoofer 
- Klippel® optimized 
- Efficient downfire technology 
- Perfect solution for extremely flat spare wheel recesses 
- No cut-out in the original trunk floor panel required 
- High power 10 woofer 
- Reinforced paper cone 
- Class AB Mosfet amplifier 
- High-Level Input with Auto-On 

 

Due to limited space in most of modern compact sized cars, many customers refuse to occupy the vehicle´s trunk with projecting and excessive subwoofer enclosures. However, they wish to have more bass from the car´s audio system. This was one of the reasons to develop a space saving subwoofer fitting the spare wheel recess. The new GZCS series subwoofer enclosure comes with a down firing flat 25 cm / 10” paper cone driver in a passive box as well as in an active version that includes a powerful amplifier with high- and low-level inputs. Specially shaped, the internal volume of the extremely flat box with about 15 liters / 0.52 cu ft remains sufficiently sized to provide a deep and substantial bass reproduction, fulfilling demands of sophisticated customers. 

The unique down firing principle of the GZCS 10SUB provides not only extended low frequency reproduction but makes it unnecessary to cut out nor to change the floor mat or plate of the trunk in any way compared to most of the competitor subwoofer solutions on the market. This makes the installation very simply, invisible and revertible in case of leasing vehicles. 

The sealed wooden enclosure with black carpet all around and a white logo stitch on top is just 12 cm / 4.7” high, offers flat rubber stands and can be fixed through the centered port. The 2x 2 Ohm subwoofer is capable of handling up to 300 Watt max. and matches perfectly the 300 Watt amplifier of the active version that includes a low pass filter with a range of 30 to 120 Hz.

Ny versjon av bestselgeren GZIB 2.300BR som hadde overlegen lydkvalitet i forhold til pris. Denne nye modellen har nye subwoofere som er optimalisert med Klippel. De har jevn impedansrespons, god følsomhet og god effekthåndtering. Dette gir god lydkvalitet og mye bass med veldig moderat forsterkerkraft. Nye bedre basselementer fortjener også et bedre kabinett. Tidligere versjon var så bra at det var vanskelig å gjøre det bedre. Løsningen var å finne på ny porttype. Dette kabinettet bruker EFP-port (Enchanced Flow Port). Den har utforming som en aeroport. Dette gir betydelig bedre luftstrøm uten bivirkninger. Mer luft gjennom porten = mer bass! Til tross for bedre luftstrøm i samme størrelse, er tuningfrekvensen den samme enn før. Det gir en veldig jevn bassrespons fra 20-60 Hz. Hvis du leter etter en basskasse som gir deg god lydkvalitet og mye bass med moderat forsterkerkraft så er dette rette valget.

Ekstra info: 
- High quality spare wheel active subwoofer 
- Klippel® optimized 
- Efficient downfire technology 
- Perfect solution for extremely flat spare wheel recesses 
- No cut-out in the original trunk floor panel required 
- High power 10 woofer 
- Reinforced paper cone 
- Class AB Mosfet amplifier 
- High-Level Input with Auto-On 

 

Due to limited space in most of modern compact sized cars, many customers refuse to occupy the vehicle´s trunk with projecting and excessive subwoofer enclosures. However, they wish to have more bass from the car´s audio system. This was one of the reasons to develop a space saving subwoofer fitting the spare wheel recess. The new GZCS series subwoofer enclosure comes with a down firing flat 25 cm / 10” paper cone driver in a passive box as well as in an active version that includes a powerful amplifier with high- and low-level inputs. Specially shaped, the internal volume of the extremely flat box with about 15 liters / 0.52 cu ft remains sufficiently sized to provide a deep and substantial bass reproduction, fulfilling demands of sophisticated customers. 

The unique down firing principle of the GZCS 10SUB provides not only extended low frequency reproduction but makes it unnecessary to cut out nor to change the floor mat or plate of the trunk in any way compared to most of the competitor subwoofer solutions on the market. This makes the installation very simply, invisible and revertible in case of leasing vehicles. 

The sealed wooden enclosure with black carpet all around and a white logo stitch on top is just 12 cm / 4.7” high, offers flat rubber stands and can be fixed through the centered port. The 2x 2 Ohm subwoofer is capable of handling up to 300 Watt max. and matches perfectly the 300 Watt amplifier of the active version that includes a low pass filter with a range of 30 to 120 Hz.

Kompakt i størrelse, men enorm i lyd. Basskassene i K serien fra Helix viser ingen nåde når de kraftige basslagene begeistrer deg. 

 
Mye teknisk finesse var nødvendig for å oppfylle kravene til både SPL-junkier og audiofile musikkelskere samtidig. Utformingen av downfire-subwooferen er rettet mot å bruke gulvet som refleksflate. Det tillater også en flatere design slik at wooferen kan lagres under det falske gulvet i bagasjerommet for å spare plass. 

 
Med steinharde høyttalermembraner og kraftige talespoler forvandles enkelt forsterkerens kraft til mye lydtrykk uten å ignorere verken akustiske detaljer eller sonisk presisjon. 

 
Designet med dobbel talespole gir større fleksibilitet når du velger en passende forsterker. Uansett om det er 1 x 4 ohm, 2 x 2 ohm eller 1 x 1 ohm - disse "dypbass garantørene" gjør enhver konfigurasjon enkel.

Due to limited space in most of modern compact sized cars, many customers refuse to occupy the vehicle´s trunk with projecting and excessive subwoofer enclosures. However, they wish to have more bass from the car´s audio system. This was one of the reasons to develop a space saving subwoofer fitting the spare wheel recess. The new GZCS series subwoofer enclosure comes with a down firing flat 25 cm / 10” paper cone driver in a passive box as well as in an active version that includes a powerful amplifier with high- and low-level inputs. Specially shaped, the internal volume of the extremely flat box with about 15 liters / 0.52 cu ft remains sufficiently sized to provide a deep and substantial bass reproduction, fulfilling demands of sophisticated customers. 

The unique down firing principle of the GZCS 10SUB provides not only extended low frequency reproduction but makes it unnecessary to cut out nor to change the floor mat or plate of the trunk in any way compared to most of the competitor subwoofer solutions on the market. This makes the installation very simply, invisible and revertible in case of leasing vehicles. 

The sealed wooden enclosure with black carpet all around and a white logo stitch on top is just 12 cm / 4.7” high, offers flat rubber stands and can be fixed through the centered port. The 2x 2 Ohm subwoofer is capable of handling up to 300 Watt max. and matches perfectly the 300 Watt amplifier of the active version that includes a low pass filter with a range of 40 to 160 Hz.

It is with great excitement that we announce the immediate release of the brand new 1506 Power Tuned Subwoofer, our smallest addition to their growing arsenal of ESP equipped subwoofers. If you need big woofer bass, but have a limited build area, the Power Tuned 1506 ESP is your new best friend. At 6.5 inches, the 1506 is a perfect solution for small space applications such as under and behind seats or tucked away in consoles and other compartments. 

As with its bigger brothers, the 1506 ESP is designed to accommodate today’s high excursion listening styles with larger diameter suspensions and deeper frames compared to standard sub designs, as well as proprietary surrounds and cones to fully take advantage of the increased geometries. Additionally, the 1506 ESP features an optimized drive circuit with a 2" high-temp voice coil and a 20mm top plate, giving the 1506 the power handling and coil control to get loud and play clean. All ESP subs are built to truly maximize performance in their designated size classes thanks to features like: 

 – The CFB composition employs a potent carbon fiber based cocktail to give you the highest strength to weight ratio of any pulp cone in the industry. 

 – Provides the ultimate in linear control at high excursion while still allowing for dynamic sounding bass reproduction. The control ribs are compressed to a lesser density than the main surround body to allow for a continuously variable control system. The harder you drive it the more control you get. 

 – Each suspension is tuned for specific performance traits, e.g. High Definition, Power Handling, X-Stiff Control. 

 – Maximizes spider diameter, cone diameter, suspension excursion, works as a secondary shorting ring and provides additional heat sinking for better heat flow from the coil.

The 9900s are the go to subwoofers for the demanding bassaholic with a profound interest in physics. Entertaining minds will revel in the endless system design possibilities deliverable with these precision low-frequency devices. Originally coined The Beast, the 9900s first appeared on the market in the early 2000s. It took a brief hiatus, but now it’s back and more beastly than ever. The latest iteration was developed in response to the recent explosion in ultra-low-frequency music. These subwoofers were designed to provide long-term power handling, with accuracy, and high excursion capabilities. It’s been optimized for a 1500 – 2500 watt power band with the ability able to handle bursts of up to 10,000 watts. One look at the 9900 motor and you see why we call it the beast. It boasts 3 inches of magnet cross-section, over a 10" OD, and weighs in at 70 pounds (motor only). The traditionally tight DD magnet gap drives a 4" flat wound aluminum voice coil to a peak excursion in excess of 3 inches while keeping enough turns in the gap to maintain power and control. The 9900 Series features our Evolution Subwoofer Package (ESP). ESP equipped drivers sport larger diameter suspensions and deeper frames than standard subs and exclusive surround and cone designs. ESP subs are truly built to maximize performance in their designated size class. The 9900 Series comes standard with an oversized dry finish black composite dust cap, red logo, and treated pulp cone, but it can be optioned out with alternative composite dust caps, composite cones, powder coated frames, supercharging, and a multitude of logo options to give your sub a personalized look and/or added performance for a specific application.

e like European! DD Audio and European distributor AI Group developed together a special model subwoofer to European market only. One of a kind subwoofer that has high sensitivity to give out more bass per every single watt used. Unlike other high sensitivity subs, 600e subs have also LOW FS to give REAL BASS and not only high frequency burps at the competitions. And of course with a price tag that is suitable for everyone. Newly designed T-yoke has solution that improves air flow and helps voice coil to stay cool. And as a very welcome bonus it also smoothens impedance curve and gives higher sensitivity. 700-series deep frame with big spiders makes it possible that these subwoofers have longer mechanical travel. Motor is a little bigger than regular 600 series has, and voice coils are Made In USA high temp-voice coils. With 600e you will definitely get more bass for your money than ever before!

Often imitated but never duplicated, the 9500 has long been a staple of our subwoofer line and has been featured in many of the world’s loudest systems. These subs are capable of easily handling 1000-2000 watts of continuous power and bursts as high as 8000 watts. Just as you would expect these bad boys are equipped with all sorts of awesome stuff such as EROM and V-ROM surrounds, Free Flow motor cooling, double slit formers, eight layer aluminum voice coils, 28mm magnetic gaps, cast aluminum frames, rigid non-pressed cones, and our multi-layer spider system. The 9500 Series features our Evolution Subwoofer Package (ESP). ESP equipped drivers sport larger diameter suspensions and deeper frames than standard subs and exclusive surround and cone designs. ESP subs are truly built to maximize performance in their designated size class. The 9500 Series comes standard with an oversized dry finish black composite dust cap, red logo, and treated pulp cone, but it can be optioned out with alternative composite dust caps, composite cones, powder coated frames, supercharging, and a multitude of logo options to give your sub a personalized look and/or added performance for a specific application.

"M"-profil "W" sandwichmembran 

Den nye, patenterte, "M"-profilmembranen er resultatet av mange års forskning og vår kompetanse innen materialer og deres geometri. Den innovative M-profilen, laget av et enkelt stykke, betyr at den er utrolig stiv og perfekt kombinerer de tre kriteriene som er viktige for å skape et "ideelt" høyttalerelement: stivhet, letthet og demping. Resultatet er en ekstremt lineær frekvensrespons, lav forvrengningsrate og bedre lyddispersjon. 

Når du lytter, gir UTOPIA M slående realisme og detaljnivå som transporterer deg inn i selve hjertet av musikken.
